## Product Overview

Beach Concierge is a progressive web-app (PWA) delivering a full VIP concierge experience across Dubai's JBR–Kite Beach coastal strip. Users locate themselves via GPS or tap their **beach grid** (e.g. `BEACH-B3`) and receive real-time delivery of food, beverage, premium equipment, and curated experiences.

**Core capabilities:**

| Module | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| 🛒 **Cart & Checkout** | Multi-catalogue ordering (menu, equipment, experiences) with RAF-batched UI updates |
| ☀️ **Live Weather** | Real-time temperature, UV index, wave height, sea temp via Open-Meteo |
| 🏅 **Loyalty Engine** | 8 VIP tiers with automated service-fee waivers at upper tiers |
| 💧 **Hydration Tracker** | Push-to-order integration with 30-minute sun-exposure alerts |
| 🎨 **Tan-Tone Scanner** | `getUserMedia` + canvas pixel analysis with Fitzpatrick-scale classification |
| 🔊 **Noise Heatmap** | Crowd-sourced dB readings via Web Audio API, grid-keyed to localStorage |
| 🎤 **Voice Ordering** | Web Speech API integration with Hebrew, Arabic, and English recognition |
| 🌐 **Full i18n** | Hebrew · Arabic · Russian · Spanish · French · English (RTL-aware) |

