         *
         * Data sources:
         *   - Current weather + UV: Open-Meteo forecast API (free, no key required)
         *   - City name: Nominatim reverse-geocode (OpenStreetMap, free)
         *   - Wave height / sea temperature: Open-Meteo Marine API
