         * requested timezone. We pass `timezone=auto` so the array aligns with
         * local Dubai time (UTC+4). We then index with the current local hour
         * offset by APP_CONFIG.DUBAI_UTC_OFFSET_H to ensure the correct UV reading
         * regardless of the user's device timezone.
         *
